<h1>About Us</h1>
<pre>Cinema club organizes screening of latest 
movies at <b>Convocation Hall,</b> with a size of 
around 1800 seats with the best projector in 
the city. These screenings(which are free of 
cost, by the way)are met with much fanfare in 
a Convo bottled down to its full capacity.</pre>
